    ## Response

    I always hope my work will inspire people to think about their medium and tools differently and to encourage them to experiment with what‚Äôs possible.

    The response has been overwhelming and it‚Äôs truly wonderful to see people discovering and enjoying the site. I‚Äôm so grateful for everyone‚Äôs kind and encouraging words.

    One piece of feedback I received is that a lot of people don‚Äôt resize their browsers at all. That‚Äôs true! And it‚Äôs totally okay. The site is still functional even if you don‚Äôt know any of the other layouts exist. Well, to be fair, there is one layout that would make for a super confusing experience (*Stranger Things* fans might know which one I‚Äôm talking about). But with my audience in mind, I figured risk was low.

    With most of my work, there are people who ask ‚ÄúWhy do this?‚Äù I have another post in the works that dives into the many reasons, but for now: sometimes it‚Äôs fun to do things that are weird.

    Thanks for checking out the site. It means the world.

